{"tid":1982521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有link］對於抗爭既歌曲 我感到痛心","createTime":"2020-04-21T09:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:28:29.000Z","uid":336400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37c39f7d874ac0491387ce9f42372be2fa7bf25c","tid":1982521,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"最近都聽返好多上年年尾既抗爭歌<br />\n我最中意既三首係 「願榮光歸香港」「香港人」「試問誰還未發聲」<br />\n個人覺得啲歌好重要 佢地承載香港人既心聲，所以啲歌大部分都係社會運動最狂熱既時期出產。<br />\n過去都一直慨嘆抗爭既歌少左出 但啱啱再聽「願榮光歸香港」，更加覺得可惜嘅係 好似冇乜人有再聽呢啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單係願榮光歸香港呢首歌，原來有手足係今年二月同三月都有製作。但令我驚訝既係 觀看次數只係得三萬多，相比起七個月前製作既願榮光歸香港的四百幾萬人觀看，相差超過100倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先再聽 真心聽到喊 因為啲歌真係代表着香港人嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />更加提醒我願榮光歸香港 mv入面抗爭既畫面係實在的 黑警打人嘅畫面更加係有血有肉的 我哋真係要繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><em>希望大家可以聽以下曾經耳熟能詳既歌曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提醒自己 革命尚未成功 更加希望可以藉此po呼喚曾經委身投入抗爭既每個香港人 <strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要醒了</span></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要行返出嚟 繼續反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />面對中共既打壓 我地唔係坐以待斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人 反抗</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦希望大家支持抗爭歌曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地係承載香港人既心聲 一種抗爭既意識</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qmhnu3cvcEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQmhnu3cvcEY&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d352f520\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qmhnu3cvcEY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-d3Qyh5BVr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-d3Qyh5BVr0&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a118f628\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-d3Qyh5BVr0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BLZQHPQg-Jc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBLZQHPQg-Jc&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3d4f04c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BLZQHPQg-Jc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=79b3779c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoUIDL4SB60g&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=2e52251f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tmrQDAXt_SY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtmrQDAXt_SY&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a3249c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tmrQDAXt_SY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zhQIOfDQdCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzhQIOfDQdCo&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=847c6c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zhQIOfDQdCo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o8KX0PboIvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo8KX0PboIvU&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=65fa78d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o8KX0PboIvU</a>"},{"pid":"2a033f92a345ab164e667f3cf65de0edf9b59e58","tid":1982521,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"153acf9ba25c8cf0203a18df5ccc18c1bc754cea","tid":1982521,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"06707d53fbe596b1fc1d1c072a98e24ff8c42c7a","tid":1982521,"uid":336400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT